description: Okay, OKC.We’re pleased to introduce you to YUM PIG: the quirky trailer that’s serving up porky dishes that you are sure to dig. You must try their criminally delicious ‘Original’: Fry Bread topped with Pulled Pork Butt, OJ Marinade, Apple-Garlic Coleslaw, and their World Famous BBQ Sauce. Their Rosemary Pulled Pork Butt on a Garlic Gnocchi Waffle, topped with Shoestring Potatoes is also where it's at. Mmmm, once you pig out on this pork of perfection, you too will become a major fan of this YUM!
name: Yum Pig
